<div id="hero">
  <div class="hero-text">
    <h1>Welcome to Hipster Parrot.</h1>
    <h2>Like Twitter, but before it was cool.</h2>
    <%= link_to 'Sign Up', new_user_path, class: "btn btn-success btn-lg" %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h3>Mainstream</h3>
      <p>The Mainstream is a global feed, where everyone's posts are shown. Some posts are cool. Others, maybe not.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h3>The Deck</h3>
      <p>The Deck is your personal feed. Only posts by people you follow will be shown.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h3>Ratio</h3>
      <p>Your ratio of followers to following. The higher the better.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>